ox the new version to be released soon includes a new command for automating this windows program start ftp archives for the mentioned programs all these archives have several mirror sites simtel oak oakland edu filutl hfm zip gif vpic e zip garbo garbo uwasa fi dirutil hfm zip cica ftp cica indiana edu util run zip andreas helke molekulare genetik universitaet heidelberg germany email un ef genius embnet dkfz heidelberg de the header of this posting does not contain a valid smtp mail address
